<p>The Site has implemented technical procedures to protect personal information from loss, misuse or alteration when it is under the Site’s control by using encryption and other security measures.</p>
<p>Despite the Company’s reasonable efforts to protect personal information, the Company cannot guaranty the personal information will not be accessed, disclosed, altered or destroyed.</p>
